<paragraph blockId="1.[227,1512,296,2426]" pageId="1" pageNumber="245">
Einen Schritt weiter geht Kennedy (Ohio Journ. Sei. 21, 1920,. p. 2 1, 25f.), indem er das bisher wenig bekannte, von de Selys zur Legion 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Selys" authorityYear="1862" box="[365,541,1521,1557]" class="Insecta" family="Megapodagrionidae" genus="Podagrion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Odonata" pageId="1" pageNumber="245" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[365,541,1521,1557]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="245">Podagrion</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
gestellte, neotropische Genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hagen" authorityYear="1862" box="[1063,1227,1521,1557]" class="Insecta" family="Perilestidae" genus="Perilestes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Odonata" pageId="1" pageNumber="245" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1063,1227,1521,1557]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="245">Perilestes</emphasis>
